      "title": "Incidence and prevention of epithelial growth within the interface after laser in situ keratomileusis",
      "abstract": "Purpose.To analyze the incidence of epithelial growth within the interface after laser in situ keratomileusis (LASIK) and describe a technique that may prevent its occurrence.Methods.Results were reviewed for all LASIK procedures performed by two surgeons using identical surgical technique with eith"
